sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Controller
    participant Service
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant MQ as Kafka
    participant ES as Elasticsearch
    
    Note over User, ES: 核心流程：发帖与搜索同步 (异步解耦)
    
    User->>Controller: 1. 发布帖子 (Title, Content)
    Controller->>Service: 2. 调用业务方法
    Service->>Service: 2.1 敏感词过滤 (Trie Tree)
    Service->>DB: 2.2 保存帖子数据
    DB-->>Service: Success
    
    Service->>MQ: 3. 发送 "发帖事件" (异步)
    MQ-->>Service: ACK
    
    Service-->>Controller: 返回结果
    Controller-->>User: 响应 "发布成功"
    
    par 异步处理 (解耦)
        MQ->>Service: 4. 消费 "发帖事件" (EventConsumer)
        Service->>ES: 5. 将帖子保存到索引库 (Elasticsearch)
        ES-->>Service: Success
    end
